Author: TotallyNotARadar
Text: Going home always makes my ED worse. Something about being in my old bedroom makes me remember all the insane bullshit I pulled in high school and I get going with the crazy thoughts. It's going to be weird though because I'm already on my bullshit because of finals and stress so who knows. Not looking forward to it tbh

Author: sapphosviolet
Text: i’m so scared i’ve barely eaten and it’s finals week so not a good combination. i find that i restrict at college and binge/purge at home. my family doesn’t know anything about eating disorders and doesn’t see (over) exercise as a problem so they don’t notice that anything’s wrong.
